var e=[{id:`L2_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`YOOMINA_FENRIR_NEXT_SPECIAL`,text:{KOREA:`가끔씩, 그런 생각을 해. 신도, 인간도 이미 지나가 버린 운명을 되돌릴 수는 없다고.`,JPN:`たまに思うんだ。神も人間も、過ぎ去った運命を取り戻すことはできない。`,ENG:`I occasionally wonder. Neither god nor human can turn back a fate that has already passed.`,TWN:`有時候我會這樣想，無論是神或人，都無法改變過去的命運。`},stage:{bg:`BLACK`,bgm:`CUTSCENE_HOPE`,filter:`NCFT_NORMAL`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`YOOMINA_FENRIR_NEXT_SPECIAL`,face:`UNIT_LAUGH`},R:null}}},{id:`L3_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`YOOMINA_FENRIR_NEXT_SPECIAL`,text:{KOREA:`하지만 이 선택에 후회는 없어. 그 어떤 가혹한 겨울이 닥치더라도, 나는 결국 당신을 포기하지 않을 테니까.`,JPN:`だけどこの選択に後悔はない。どんなに過酷な冬が訪れようと、私はあなたを諦められないから。`,ENG:`But I have no regrets about this choice. No matter what harsh winter may come, I will never give up on you.`,TWN:`但是我對於這個選擇不後悔。無論多麼殘酷的冬季來臨，我都不會放棄你。`},stage:{bg:`BLACK`,bgm:`CUTSCENE_HOPE`,filter:`NCFT_NORMAL`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`YOOMINA_FENRIR_NEXT_SPECIAL`,face:`UNIT_PRIDE`},R:null}}}];export{e as default};